Camcorp 0.71V
=============

Updated version of the camcorp designed to be used in the revised (2022) book study.

Changes from v0.7:

- "Unstressed" list of monosyllables restricts stressed monosyllables to *lexical categories* only.
        - policy of conservative tagging to reduce overgeneration of "possible" stress.
        - also excludes monosyllabic forms of *estre* and *avoir*.
        
